Package com.clarionmedia.infinitum.orm.sqlite.impl

Provides concrete implementations for the SQLite ORM framework.

          Description

Class Summary
SqliteBuilder Implementation of SqlBuilder for interacting with a SQLite database.
SqliteCriteria<T> Implementation of Criteria for SQLite queries.
SqliteDbHelper A helper class to manage database creation and version management.
SqliteHelperFactoryImpl Implementation of SqliteHelperFactory.
SqliteMapper This implementation of ObjectMapper provides methods to map domain models to SQLite table columns and vice versa.
SqliteModelFactory This is an implementation of ModelFactory for processing SqliteResult queries.
SqliteModelMap Concrete implementation of ModelMap representing a domain model instance mapped to a SQLite table.
SqliteResult This implementation represents a ResultSet from a SQLite database query.

SqliteTemplate An implementation of SqliteOperations.
